member.name: T:Sentry.Associates.IAssociatesServiceClient
member.summary: A specialized version of IAssociatesService that supports local in-memory caching.

member.name: P:Sentry.Associates.IAssociatesServiceClient.HasLocalCache
member.summary: Returns true if the service has a local cache that queries will be run against.

member.name: M:Sentry.Associates.IAssociatesServiceClient.LoadLocalCache(System.Boolean)
member.summary: Calls GetAllAssociates and retains the results as a local in-memory cache. Subsequent calls to this interface will return results from the cache, until ClearLocalCache is called.
member.param: Whether or not to include inactive associates in the results.
member.remarks: This method executes synchronously and could take a long time to return. Consider using the asynchronous version, BeginLoadLocalCache.

member.name: M:Sentry.Associates.IAssociatesServiceClient.ClearLocalCache
member.summary: Clears the local in-memory cache set on this instance, causing search methods to again query the web service instead of looking in the cache.

member.name: M:Sentry.Associates.IAssociatesServiceClient.BeginLoadLocalCache(System.AsyncCallback,System.Object,System.Boolean)
member.summary: Calls BeginGetAllAssociates to asynchronously retrieve all associates and will retain those results as a local in-memory cache. When your callback is invoked you must call EndLoadLocalCache to complete the operation and store the results. Subsequent calls to this interface will return results from the cache, until ClearLocalCache is called.
member.param: The method that will be called when the results are ready.
A user-specific object that will be passed along to the callback as part of the IAsyncResult.
Whether or not to include inactive associates in the results.
member.returns: The IAsyncResult representing the asynchronous operation.
member.remarks: The callback may be called on a different thread than the one calling this method.

member.name: M:Sentry.Associates.IAssociatesServiceClient.EndLoadLocalCache(System.IAsyncResult)
member.summary: Call this method from the callback supplied to BeginLoadLocalCache to complete the operation.
member.param: The IAsyncResult passed to the callback.
